videos.description: For the third time this season, Notre Dame loses a game in which it led by double digits when it falls to Virginia Tech at home 34-31. The result might have turned up the temperature on Brian Kelly's hot seat.
videos.headline: Hokies rally, hand Irish first losing season under Kelly
